OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA fine end
OL,6,Fto the day with plenty of evening
OL,7,Fsunshine and staying dry overnight.
OL,8,FLow cloud and Haar could develop
OL,9,Faround some North Sea coasts.
OL,10,
OL,11,CThursday:FMainly dry and bright and
OL,12,Fwarm or very warm inland. Low cloud
OL,13,Fand Haar could affect North Sea coasts
OL,14,Fand heavy showers perhaps breaking out
OL,15,Flater in the day.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
